explanations.description: The token often indicates words that are related to a particular domain or field, such as technology ("phishing", "bug", "hostel", "homophobic", etc.), but also appears in contexts such as ordinal numbers ("Number"), nouns that describe a contained space or relationship ("hostel", "rivalry"), or form a word with a preceding word ("hos", "Gill", "pho").
